Description
-----------
Mean and sum are computed using static/dynamic library, variables are passed from the main/driver program.

Steps for compilation
---------------------
1. make 
To generate shared and dynamic libraries and run executables.

3. make clean
To remove .o,.a and .so files.


Output
------
 Result: 
 a=2.20  b=4.40 
 Mean=3.30
 Sum=6.60 

